5:
May the Stars ever guide you down
the righteous path...
7:
You're helping us... even though
we're your enemies?!
12:
You idiots! She just beat the living
daylights out of you a second ago!
19:
Marina! We've searched the whole
ship, but we found no signs of Luca...
23:
Everyone who fell overboard has
already been rescued.
27:
There was no sign of those
creatures among the enemies,
either. Where on earth did Luca
disappear off to?
32:
All right, Forkbeard. Where'd that
woman go off to? Start talking while
you still have teeth in your mouth.
36:
How the hell am I supposed to know!
She just up and left. We're just here
cause she paid us, we don't know
who she really is!
41:
Hold on... Over there, there seems to
be a strange distortion in the light!
44:
O Sacred Light, reveal yourself to
me! Show me truth!
52: What is that thing? A submarine?
61:
I'm going after her! That ship might
disappear any minute. If we lose
sight of it now, we might never find it
again!
68:
Oh, Alky-Walky! Please take this
before you go!
76:
It's a little charm. A present from
yours truly! You ARE going with her,
aren't you?
84: Alk! Are you sure about this?
87:
Yep! You're definitely gonna need a
back-up driver, after all!
92:
When'd you go and get so
chivalrous all of a sudden? Hehe.
96:
I don't know what you're talking
about!
101: Guess we'll be going then, Alk!
106:
Yeah. Let's find Luca and bring him
back!
111:
Naska. Please get our ship moving
as well.
113: There's somewhere we need to go.
117:
It should be right up ahead! Just
keep going until we run into it—we'll
think about what to do later!
119:
If it comes down to it, I'll be ready to
blow the whole place sky-high.
131:
Did I say stop?! Keep going until you
get to that submarine!
136: I... I have to do this.
140:
It's all up to me now! I'm coming,
Luca!
146:
There has to be an entrance
somewhere around here...
152:
Ouch, that hurts...
At least I managed to make my way
inside.
156:
Well, I can't say I didn't expect these
guys to show up.
159:
But don't think I'm gonna let you
stand in my way!
